Medical Appointment Card Generator System
ğŸ“‹ Overview
A complete web system for generating and managing medical appointment cards in printable A4 format. The application allows creation, customization, saving, and printing of multiple medical appointment cards completely offline.

âœ¨ Key Features
ğŸ¨ Flexible Layouts
5 layout configurations: 1, 2, 4, 6, or 8 cards per A4 sheet

Automatic sizing: Texts and logos automatically adjust based on layout

Real-time preview: WYSIWYG preview of appointment cards

ğŸ’¾ Local Storage System
Saved logos: Upload and locally store logos for reuse

Saved addresses: Library of frequently used addresses

Saved patients: Database of patient names for quick filling

Saved hospitals: List of frequently used hospitals/clinics

ğŸ”„ Advanced Features
Copy and paste between cards: Copy data from one card to another

Individual logos per card: Each card can have its own specific logo

Data validation: Date, time, and required field validation

Automatic formatting: Automatic capitalization of names and addresses

ğŸ“¤ Multiple Export Options
Direct printing: Optimized for A4 sheet printing

PDF download: High-quality PDF generation

