ğŸš€ How to Use
1. Initial Setup
Open appointment_3.1.html in any modern browser

No installation required - works completely offline

2. Basic Customization
Select desired layout (1, 2, 4, 6, or 8 cards)

Fill in general data:

Patient name (can save for reuse)

Hospital/Clinic (can save for reuse)

Medical specialty

Address (can save for reuse)

Default date and time

Upload a logo (optional)

3. Individual Editing
Click any card to edit its specific data

Click the logo to load an individual logo for that card

Use the yellow badge (ğŸ“‹) to copy data between cards

4. Saving and Reuse
ğŸ’¾ button in each field: saves current value for future use

Autocomplete: Suggests saved values while typing

Visible library: All saved items appear below the fields

5. Export Options
Print now: Optimized A4 printing

Download PDF: High-quality PDF download

Download image: PNG format download

ğŸ’¡ Tips and Shortcuts
Enter in fields: Quick save changes

ESC: Closes any open modal

Hover over yellow badge: Shows "Copy this card"

Click yellow badge: Copies the card to paste elsewhere

Click a card with a copied card: Pastes copied data

ğŸ”’ Security and Privacy Features
Completely offline: No data sent to external servers

Local storage: Data saved only in user's browser

Full control: User manages all saved data

Easy cleanup: Buttons to clear each type of saved data

ğŸ¨ Customization
Colors: Professional blue scheme for medical field

Typography: Segoe UI font for better readability

Responsiveness: Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile

Accessibility: Proper contrast and keyboard navigation

